    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014this car is a total showstopper! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dings, and the interior is still smelling fresh. It\u2019s been kept in a garage and driven very gently, so it runs like an absolute dream. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty as much as I have. Come see it for yourself\u2014you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
