      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear 333 hp. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M Differential Lock. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement with VAC coated bearings. The rear subframe has been reinforced with TMS plates, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, providing the precise turn-in and feedback expected of an unmolested chassis. This is a collector-grade vehicle with zero aftermarket modifications and a documented service history.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
