    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, matched by spotless alloy wheels wrapped in premium tires. Inside, the cabin retains that new-car aroma, featuring supple, untouched leather seating and a dashboard free of any wear or sun damage. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; the engine runs with whisper-quiet precision, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. Complete with a full service history and all original keys/manuals, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
